body.name: DOGIBIXO Queen Size Bed Frame with LED Lights, Upholstered Bed Frame with Wingback Diamond Tufted Headboard, Wood Slats Support, Noise-Free, Easy Assembly, No Box Spring Needed, Beige
features: ELEGANT BED FRAME WITH SMART LED LIGHTS: Nailhead trim wingback headboard is paired with velvet fabric for a sleek, skin-friendly contemporary upholstered bed frame. Elegant geometric shapes paired with simple beige are easy to integrate into your new housewarming home! The colorful light bed frame lights up your room at night, so that you and your family don't have to endure the dark room anymore.

STURDY PLATFORM BED: The upholstered wooden structure bed frame consists of 12 high-quality solid wood slats and 9 supporting legs. The overall structure allows the platform bed frame to be more evenly loaded and provide 1000 lbs of support for your mattress! The mattress no longer has to worry about sagging, providing you and your family with a safe and comfortable sleeping environment.

NOISE FREE DESIGN: Both sides of the gray bed frame are designed with Velcro, which can firmly fix the 12 plank support slats to prevent creaking sound! There are soft pads under each support leg of the modern upholstered bed frame to keep the floor from being scratched and again to reduce noise generation! The DOGIBIXO led bed frame can give your daughter, lover, relatives or friends a restful and colorful night!

EASY TO ASSEMBLE: Package comes with all parts, no extra tools required. We provide enough detailed instructions to help you assemble the queen upholstered bed frame quickly and accurately, each part has part numbers and operation steps explained! As long as you follow the instructions, putting it together is very easy. Please believe in your hands-on ability and experience the fun and fulfillment of assembling the modern bed frame yourself!

NO BOX SPRING REQUIRED & NICE SERVICE: The mattress can be placed directly on the wooded slats of the grey bed frame, no need to buy additional box springs, you can save more money and time! DOGIBIXO bed frame warranty: ① Replace any missing or damaged parts. ② Reasonable compensation or full refund for quality and transportation problems. ③ 24-hour after-sales customer service is online to solve your problems and bring you a good shopping experience.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute and good quality
reviews.reviewText: It is cute and good quality for this price. I have used this bed frame for 3 months, and it is still working great for me. I like it because it is very easy to assemble. Also it is well designed and made of sturdy hardwood to support mattress, so it doesn’t need to buy box spring. Very good quality and convenient. I highly recommend it.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars perfect for my bedroom

The attention to detail in the design is evident, contributing to the overall aesthetic appeal of the bed frame.Assembly was surprisingly easy, thanks to the thoughtful design and clear instructions provided. I appreciate that no box spring is needed, simplifying the setup process and saving both time and effort.The LED lights are a unique and stylish feature that sets this bed frame apart. The ability to adjust the lighting adds a customizable touch, allowing me to create the perfect ambiance for different moods.One noteworthy aspect of the DOGIBIXO bed frame is its claim to be noise-free, and I can attest that it lives up to this promise. Its combination of elegant design, easy assembly, wood slats support, LED lights, and noise-free functionality make it a standout choice for anyone in search of a quality bed frame. I highly recommend it for those looking to enhance both the style and comfort of their bedroom.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Arrived dirty, damaged,& with dirty shoe prints
reviews.reviewText: I’m disappointed in this bed to say the least. Was so excited to get this for my daughter and upon opening the box I saw it looked dingy. I unwrapped the plastic thinking it was just that. But no. The fabric itself is dirty. There is even a shoe print where someone stepped on the panel. There are dents and dings everywhere. The legs are extremely flimsy and anticipate they will break off very soon. The side boards in also concerned about. Putting in the bolts I could hear the wood crack when they were barely tightened. Don’t let the LED lights persuade you. Buy a string separate for $15 and get the same results. If I try to return, it would cost me more money than it’s worth, so there goes $180 out the window. Some say you get ehat you paid for, but I bought a bed for $90 at Walmart that lasted 7yrs until I sold it to “upgrade” to this one. I say don’t waste your money on this.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Absolute best decision!!
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for a beige bedframe but I also wanted it to have lights connected. I loved this one because the lights were at the top. It came with a remote and I can attach the lights to an app. There are so many colors I can use to set that mood(Can you tell that is my favorite part)Very good quality for the price! I did not put together myself, I used Task Rabbit but it was very quick for him to put together and he put it together by himself. If you are looking for a classy, quality product I would highly recommend purchasing this. You wont be disappointed!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Attractive, well-constructed bed!
reviews.reviewText: This bed was so much better than I expected for the price. Very affordable. The headboard is well-constructed and attractive, soft and great color. It took my daughter and me longer than expected to assemble but directions were pretty clear. The bed was closer to the ground than expected but my daughter loves it. She especially loves the lights.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Affordable and cute!
reviews.reviewText: A little short, but very soft and easy to assemble! It was perfect for our small room and worth the price! Highly recommend

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful and strong
reviews.reviewText: Very clean, firm and easy to assemble. The room is coming together and we are using the bed frame as inspiration.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Easy Assembly but Beware of Hardware
reviews.reviewText: Beds was easy to assemble, what you would expect for the cost. Several parts but instructions were clear and easy to follow. However, the bolts in the hardware packs were completely rusted and had residue all over them. Needless to say this made assembling the white fabric bed frame a little challenging. We had to be extremely careful and it took two of us.. one to hold the frame and one to handle the hardware so as to not get the red rust particles all over the bed. For the money it is a nice looking bed and seems sturdy enough. The lights were a little disappointing, just a 6' led sticky strip to sit on the top of the headboard.
